node.text: Pinks 'N' Purps a week and a half since transplant...looks like they're ready to flip now.  These, 180 seed plants, are going to be open pollinated for this preservation run.  I will also be selecting males and females for future directional breeding as well as for making some Purple type hybrids.  Should be the start of a very fun project. 🌱🌱🌱
